	  <concept id="i1066629"
            ditaarch:DITAArchVersion="1.3"
            class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
		    <title class="- topic/title ">
			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">50.206</ph> Solicitation provisions and contract clause.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2988e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3002e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045118.dita#i1045118"
                        base="i1045118"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.250-2</xref>, SAFETY Act Coverage Not Applicable, in solicitations if-</p>
					          <ol id="d2988e26" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e30" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                The agency consulted with DHS on a questionable case of SAFETY Act applicability to an acquisition in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1066578.dita#i1066578"
                              base="i1066578"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">50.205-1</xref>(a), and after the consultation, the agency has determined that SAFETY Act protection is not applicable for the acquisition; or</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e42" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                DHS has denied approval of a pre-qualification designation notice.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3002e53" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d2988e59" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e63" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045131.dita#i1045131"
                              base="i1045131"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-3</xref>, SAFETY Act Block Designation/Certification, in a solicitation when DHS has issued a block designation/certification for the solicited technologies.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e75" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Use the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045131.dita#i1045131"
                              base="i1045131"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-3</xref> with its Alternate I when contingent offers are authorized in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1066610.dita#i1066610"
                              base="i1066610"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">50.205-3</xref>.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e90" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Use the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045131.dita#i1045131"
                              base="i1045131"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-3</xref> with its Alternate II when offers presuming SAFETY Act designation or certification are authorized in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1066619.dita#i1066619"
                              base="i1066619"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">50.205-4</xref>. If this alternate is used, the contracting officer may increase the number of days within which offerors must submit their SAFETY Act designation or certification application.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li props="Runin" class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3002e107" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            
					          </p>
					          <ol id="d2988e113" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e117" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Insert the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045186.dita#i1045186"
                              base="i1045186"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-4</xref>, SAFETY Act Pre-qualification Designation Notice, in a solicitation for which DHS has issued a pre-qualification designation notice.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e129" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Use the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045186.dita#i1045186"
                              base="i1045186"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-4</xref> with its Alternate I when contingent offers are authorized in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1066610.dita#i1066610"
                              base="i1066610"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">50.205-3</xref>.</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e144" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                Use the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045186.dita#i1045186"
                              base="i1045186"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-4</xref> with its Alternate II when offers presuming SAFETY Act designation or certification are authorized in accordance with <xref href="FAR-i1066619.dita#i1066619"
                              base="i1066619"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">50.205-4</xref>. If this alternate is used, the contracting officer may increase the number of days within which offerors must submit their SAFETY Act designation or certification application.</p>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d3002e161" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Insert the clause at <xref href="FAR-i1045243.dita#i1045243"
                        base="i1045243"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">52.250-5</xref>, SAFETY Act-Equitable Adjustment-</p>
					          <ol id="d2988e170" class="- topic/ol ">
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e174" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                In the solicitation, if the provision at <xref href="FAR-i1045131.dita#i1045131"
                              base="i1045131"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-3</xref> or <xref href="FAR-i1045186.dita#i1045186"
                              base="i1045186"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">52.250-4</xref> is used with its Alternate II; and</p>
						            </li>
						            <li class="- topic/li ">
							              <p id="d3002e189" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
                        
								                In any resultant contract, if DHS has not issued SAFETY Act designation or certification to the successful offeror before contract award.</p>
							              <p id="d3002e195" class="- topic/p "/>
						            </li>
					          </ol>
				        </li>
			      </ol>
